graph TD
    Identify[Asset Identification & Classification] --> Vulnerability[Threat & Vulnerability Discovery]
    Vulnerability --> Analyze[Calculate Risk Score: Likelihood x Impact]
    Analyze --> Evaluate[Compare Against Executive Risk Appetite Threshold]

    Evaluate -->|Risk Above Threshold| Mitigate[Risk Treatment Options]
    Evaluate -->|Risk Within Threshold| Accept[Formally Accept Risk & Log in Registry]

    Mitigate --> Avoid[Avoid: Discontinue Activity]
    Mitigate --> Transfer[Transfer: Buy Cyber Insurance]
    Mitigate --> Reduce[Reduce: Implement Engineering Controls]

    Avoid --> Reassess[Continuous Verification & Auditing]
    Transfer --> Reassess
    Reduce --> Reassess
    Accept --> Reassess
    Reassess -->|New Threat vectors Emerged| Identify

    style Identify fill:#1e3a8a,stroke:#3b82f6,stroke-width:1px,color:#fff
    style Evaluate fill:#b45309,stroke:#f59e0b,stroke-width:2px,color:#fff
    style Mitigate fill:#0f766e,stroke:#14b8a6,stroke-width:2px,color:#fff
    style Accept fill:#4b5563,stroke:#9ca3af,stroke-width:1px,color:#fff